  <summary date="2019-06-19T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Reward Work Act 

This bill prohibits issuers from purchasing their own securities on a national exchange. The bill also requires one-third of&#160;an issuer's&#160;board of directors&#160;to be&#160;elected by employees in order&#160;for the issuer to be allowed&#160;to register securities.</summary>
